formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
Remarks : 1A).We have verified copy of the KYC produced before us. In some of the cases KYC was misplaced from the promoter?s office. Another copy is requested by the promoter, however, to comply the time line we are submitting the same by entering dummy ID as AAAAA0000A and Phone No. as 9999999999. As without it we cannot submit the return online. The Promoter has assured to produce it as early as possible and before end of the next quarter they will submit the same. 1B).We have verified information based on the books of accounts and other evidence produced before us. We could able to comment on financial transaction only for other information we have relied on information produced by the promoter of the project. We do not have competence to comment on the carpet area and other measurement mentioned in the certificate. For the same we have relied on the information produce by the management/promoter of the project.
2. Technical data as to measurement and others are taken as provided by the Architect and Engineer to the management.
3.  Bank Balance are subject to reconciliation. Issued cheques which are not deposited or under clearing are considered as paid. Similarly Cheques received and not cleared are taken as received. Balance are verified and taken as per books of accounts. 
4.IN Point no.7  of Rera Form-3 (CA Certificate) as Amount withdrawn till date of this certificate as per the Books of Accounts and Bank Statement is taken as per Rera Account (70%) kindly note this.
5. Some of the heads are Interchanged kindly Note this.
6.Secure Loan is Fully closed and NOC Upload in the Loan Attachments
